      <title>Matematika Detik</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/pages/matematika-detik/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/pages/matematika-detik/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;my-6&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img src=&#34;//localhost:1313/images/uploads/whatsapp-image-2025-07-27-at-18.26.47_b8d0e08c.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Gambaran Utuh Matematika Detik&#34; class=&#34;rounded-lg shadow-lg mx-auto max-w-full h-auto&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;        &lt;figcaption class=&#34;text-center italic text-sm mt-2 text-gray-600&#34;&gt;Gambaran Utuh Matematika Detik&lt;/figcaption&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;video-responsive&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;iframe src=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/embed/ShaMdXqxwVQ&#34; frameborder=&#34;0&#34; allow=&#34;accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture&#34; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;video-responsive&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;iframe src=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/embed/SoFdamzNBdg&#34; frameborder=&#34;0&#34; allow=&#34;accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture&#34; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Matematika Detik (Second Mathematics) adalah tentang intuisi, berpikir cepat, atau blink.  Second Mathematics adalah tentang detail -operasional &amp;ldquo;your gut is your second brain&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Terinspirasi buku &amp;ldquo;Thinking Fast and Slow&amp;rdquo; (Daniel Kahneman, psikolog yang memenangkan Nobel ekonomi), Matematika Detik bukan tentang berhitung cepat, melainkan tentang berpikir cepat. &amp;ldquo;Asah intuisi, kelola dua detik pertama.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
